tiers.ability_description: Dark Side allies recover 2% Health whenever they critically hit an enemy.
Whenever enemies are damaged at the start of their turn, Hutt Cartel allies gain 2% Turn Meter.

The max cooldown of Inventive is reduced by 1. Whenever Boushh inflicts Thermal Detonators on an enemy, inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns and Hutt Cartel allies gain 10% Armor Penetration (max 70%) and 10% Turn Meter (once per turn).
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever a Scoundrel ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
At the end of any Droid ally's turn, Doctor Aphra takes a bonus turn and recovers 5% Health and Protection.
Whenever Light Side allies inflict a debuff on an enemy, they deal damage to that enemy equal to 2% of that enemy's Max Health.
Whenever Rebel Fighter allies grant a buff to another ally, that ally gains 10% Turn Meter (limit once per turn per ally).
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.
